<blockquote type="cite" class="">Yeah, any other recommendations I can give to convince the powers-that-be that immediate sun-setting of LAM/MPI would be great. &nbsp; Sometimes I feel&nbsp;like I am trying&nbsp;to fit a square peg in a round hole&nbsp;L<br class="">
